sentence: Thursday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 3,258.93.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 1.62 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 2.02 to 1 ratio.
There were 1656 advancers and 818 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 176 stocks reached a 52 week high and 9 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up .31% for the day; a total of 8.62 points.
Intuitive Surgical, Inc. ( ISRG ) had the largest percent change down (-3.82%) while Sears Holdings Corporation ( SHLD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 2.9%.
The Dow Jones index closed up .58% for the day; a total of 83.86 points.
Home Depot, Inc. (The) ( HD ) had the largest percent change down (-.73%) while Hewlett-Packard Company ( HPQ ) had the largest percent change gain rising 2.86%.
